  "contentHtml": "<p>1. <a href=\"https://x.com/MathiasChu/status/2064493902271262809\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Fable 5 describes humanity</a>.&nbsp; And <a href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/policy-on-the-ai-exponential/epf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Anthropic policy proposals, including for economics</a>.</p>\n<p>2. “Can you build a working chess board which then illustrates and can play the moves of the famous “Evergreen game”?”&nbsp; <a href=\"https://claude.ai/chat/5c708ee0-d4f5-4d55-9852-84ed15a513b9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The response</a>.&nbsp; <a href=\"https://x.com/alexolegimas/status/2065054981095366846\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Much better yet is Fable 5 explaining Riemann</a>.</p>\n<p>3. <a href=\"https://marcusnunes.substack.com/p/the-chilean-mirror-what-argentina\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Marcus Nunes on Chile vs. Argentina</a>.</p>\n<p>4. <a href=\"https://freesystems.substack.com/p/memes-doom-how-tiktokers-and-youtubers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">In the video world, AI is reasonably popular rather than hated</a>.</p>\n<p>5. <a href=\"https://x.com/jsrailton/status/2064661778978533571?s=46\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Solve for the equilibrium!</a> It is not always easy to do.</p>\n<p>6. <a href=\"https://sftw.substack.com/p/how-avocados-stopped-being-seasonal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">How avocados stopped being seasonal</a>.</p>\n<p>7. <a href=\"https://x.com/erikbryn/status/2064713648480907373\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">New Stanford program for AI economic indicators</a>.</p>\n<p>8. <a href=\"https://x.com/poperespecter1/status/2064917118311620946?s=20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Music and video for the Pope</a>.&nbsp; Or is it for Gaudi?</p>",
